abstract: >-
  This R data package provides access to texts of Peace
  Books (PB), reference reports prepared by the Historical
  Section of the British Foreign Office between 1918 and
  1919 for use by the British Delegation at the Paris Peace
  Conference in 1919. The reports were published in 1920 in
  English. The individual volumes contain reference
  information regrading geography, culture, population, and
  economy of almost all countries and territories in the
  world.
